# Web3Forms access key for the contact form.
# 1. Sign up at https://web3forms.com (verify the email you want inquiries sent to).
# 2. Copy the access key.
# 3. Set it in Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables → VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY
#    (and in a local .env file for `npm run dev`).
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key
